org.apache.giraph.metrics

类 NoOpMetricsRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yammer.metrics.core.MetricsRegistry
      • org.apache.giraph.metrics.NoOpMetricsRegistry

  • public class NoOpMetricsRegistry
extends com.yammer.metrics.core.MetricsRegistry
    An empty MetricsRegistry, used to easily turn off all metrics without affecting client code.
